blog.name: kingdomofkitten
blog.title: Jacob A.K.A. KingdomOfKitten
blog.description:
I write sometimes. I think that says a lot about my career choices.

My Twitter: https://twitter.com/KingdomOfKitten

My Letterboxd: https://letterboxd.com/kingdomofkitten/

body:
Meeting The Families: Part 8

Rie: Are you sure you have to leave now?

Retsuko: *holding bags* I’m sorry, guys, we’d love to stay further! But we gotta be at work first thing tomorrow. We were only allowed so much vacation time.

Hiroko: Ah, your boss sounds like an asshole.

Haida: Don’t remind me…*suddenly, a familiar gust of wind rushes up his back, as a familiar figure aims a wooden sword above* what the-?!

*before the sword hits his head, Hiroko grabs it, and slams it, and it’s owner to the ground….it’s Ryuu*

Riko: Ryuu, you jerk!

Hiroko: The hell is that about, punk?!

Ryuu: Shut up! I was just trying to-!

Hiroko: TRYING TO WHAT?

Harumi: *to Retsuko and Haida* IIIII think you kids need to get going.

Haida: Hehe, yeah.

Retsuko: Well, mom, dad, it was wonderful being here again. 

Rie: We always appreciate you coming by.

Ryota: And Retsuko? …thank you.

Retsuko: ….*smiles* no problem, dad.

Ryota: …I haven’t asked you yet, but any chance you can still squeeze your old man into your wedding?

Retsuko: *hugs him* Of course, dad. ^_^

Ryota: Aw. *to Ikari* Bye, little one!

Retsuko: Can you say bye-bye to grandpa?

Ikari: *instead shoves his paw in his mouth*

Ryota: *chuckles* Close enough.

Hisoka: Well, I reckon we’re gonna help them fix up this house a bit, then head on out.

Haida: Alright. *hugs his parents*

Harumi: Aw, my baby boy’s all grown up!

Haida: Mom!

Retsuko: C’mon, Haida, or else we’ll miss the train! Bye, everyone!

Haida: Oh! *follows her, out the house, and down the street, bags in hand*

Rie: Bye, Retsuko! Bye, Haida!

Ryota: Be sure to write!

Retsuko: *while they’re walking away* Don’t you have a phone?

Ryota: I kept a decade long grudge, you think I kept up with tech?

Retsuko: Heh, fair point!

*an hour later, the three are on a train, heading home*

Retsuko: *siiigh* ….you know, I didn’t expect this to go as great as it did.

Haida: Agreed…now I know so much more about you I wasn’t expecting.

Retsuko: Yeah…good, or bad?

Haida: Hmm….probably still good. In, like, a sorta exotic, kinda dangerous way….kinda sexy, actually. ;)

Retsuko: *blushes* Stop! ^^ *looking at Ikari* Did you have a good time? :)

Ikari: Aah! :D

Retsuko: That’s good! ^_^ Oh! *grabs her phone* I might need to check on Fenneko.

Haida: Oh, man! I forgot she was watching our place!

Retsuko: Me too…*gets her on FaceTime* Hey, Fenneko! …are you still in bed?

Fenneko: Ugh…yeah, I was up late last night…what do you want?

Retsuko: Well, we’re calling in, to let you know we’re coming home now! We’re just a few hours away.

Fenneko: Mrhm, alright. I kept track of the place fine, I guess…your kid makes it a bit of a mess, though. I’m surprised you let him get awa-

Tsunoda: *crawling next to Fenneko* Hmm? Who’s that, Fenny-poo?

Fenneko: *her eyes widen, as she tries to hide the phone*

Retsuko: Wha-Fenneko! *laughs* Did you have Tsunoda over?!

Haida: She did what?! :D

Retsuko: Yeah! I just saw her, on our bed!

Haida: Hey, Fenneko! You better not have had too much fun on there!

Tsunoda: Oh, we had plenty of fun last night, Haida!

Fenneko: Shut up, shut up, SHUT UP!

*the red panda and hyena laugh, as the train takes them back to their home, with one less obstacle on their path towards holy matrimony…*

OH MY GOD I AM FINALLY DONE WITH THIS ARC

For real, thank you all so much for dealing with my own procrastinating ass. I hope not to do that shit again in the future. That being said, I hope to have a small Halloween skit out sometime soon, and I have a big ol’ thing coming up. Let’s just say it involves…commissions. ;)

Until next time!

Hisoka: Well, I reckon we’re gonna help them fix up this house a bit, then head on out.

Haida: Alright. *hugs his parents*

Harumi: Aw, my baby boy’s all grown up!

Haida: Mom!

Retsuko: C’mon, Haida, or else we’ll miss the train! Bye, everyone!

Haida: Oh! *follows her, out the house, and down the street, bags in hand*

Rie: Bye, Retsuko! Bye, Haida!

Ryota: Be sure to write!

Retsuko: *while they’re walking away* Don’t you have a phone?

Ryota: I kept a decade long grudge, you think I kept up with tech?

Retsuko: Heh, fair point!

*an hour later, the three are on a train, heading home*

Retsuko: *siiigh* ….you know, I didn’t expect this to go as great as it did.

Haida: Agreed…now I know so much more about you I wasn’t expecting.

Retsuko: Yeah…good, or bad?

Haida: Hmm….probably still good. In, like, a sorta exotic, kinda dangerous way….kinda sexy, actually. ;)

Retsuko: *blushes* Stop! ^^ *looking at Ikari* Did you have a good time? :)

Ikari: Aah! :D

Retsuko: That’s good! ^_^ Oh! *grabs her phone* I might need to check on Fenneko.

Haida: Oh, man! I forgot she was watching our place!

Retsuko: Me too…*gets her on FaceTime* Hey, Fenneko! …are you still in bed?

Fenneko: Ugh…yeah, I was up late last night…what do you want?

Retsuko: Well, we’re calling in, to let you know we’re coming home now! We’re just a few hours away.

Fenneko: Mrhm, alright. I kept track of the place fine, I guess…your kid makes it a bit of a mess, though. I’m surprised you let him get awa-

Tsunoda: *crawling next to Fenneko* Hmm? Who’s that, Fenny-poo?

Fenneko: *her eyes widen, as she tries to hide the phone*

Retsuko: Wha-Fenneko! *laughs* Did you have Tsunoda over?!

Haida: She did what?! :D

Retsuko: Yeah! I just saw her, on our bed!

Haida: Hey, Fenneko! You better not have had too much fun on there!

Tsunoda: Oh, we had plenty of fun last night, Haida!

Fenneko: Shut up, shut up, SHUT UP!

*the red panda and hyena laugh, as the train takes them back to their home, with one less obstacle on their path towards holy matrimony…*

OH MY GOD I AM FINALLY DONE WITH THIS ARC

For real, thank you all so much for dealing with my own procrastinating ass. I hope not to do that shit again in the future. That being said, I hope to have a small Halloween skit out sometime soon, and I have a big ol’ thing coming up. Let’s just say it involves…commissions. ;)

Until next time!
